{
  "texts": [
    "However, for a more comprehensive evaluation of the model's performance, we should also consider the analysis results from the \"T,\" \"A,\" and \"V\" columns, as multimodal analysis provides a richer and more accurate emotional recognition by integrating various types of data.",
    "This study introduces a multimodal emotion recognition method that synergizes tensor decomposition fusion with self-supervised multitask learning.",
    "By employing Tucker decomposition, the model significantly reduces its parameter count, mitigating the risk of overfitting.",
    "Concurrently, it establishes a learning mechanism for both multimodal and unimodal tasks, incorporating the concept of label generation to capture the emotional variances across different modalities with greater precision.",
    "Experiments on public datasets such as CMU-MOSI and CMU-MOSEI have demonstrated notable performance improvements with this method."
  ]
}